This is a mirror of http://www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=4439

This Script provides a GUI only color-scheme. 

GITHUB Repository:

http://github.com/sandeepsinghmails/Dev_Delight

Screenshot:

http://github.com/sandeepsinghmails/Dev_Delight/blob/master/Images/Screenshot_1.jpeg

How To Use Dev_Delight?

Use the command ":color Dev_Delight"

How To Set Dev_Delight as your Default Color Scheme?

Add the following Line (as-it-is) to your .gvimrc File:

colorscheme Dev_Delight
